---

<Layout title={title} description={description}>
  <CategoryHero
    title={title}
    description={description}
    image="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1531986362435-16b427eb9c26"
  />

  <article class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16">
    <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none mb-16">
      <p class="lead text-xl text-gray-600">
        Kyoto's cherry blossom season transforms the ancient capital into a pink wonderland, offering photographers countless opportunities for unique shots.
      </p>
      
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mt-12 mb-6">Prime Photography Locations</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-16">
      {photoSpots.map(spot => (
        <PhotoSpot {...spot} />
      ))}
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Photography Tips</h2>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-16">
      {photographyTips.map(tip => (
        <PhotoTip {...tip} />
      ))}
    </div>

    <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
      <h2>Planning Your Visit</h2>
      <h3>Seasonal Timing</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Late March to mid-April (varies yearly)</li>
        <li>Book accommodations months in advance</li>
        <li>Follow Japanese meteorological websites for bloom forecasts</li>
      </ul>

      <h3>Photography Equipment</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Versatile zoom lens (24-70mm recommended)</li>
        <li>Macro lens for close-up blossom details</li>
        <li>Polarizing filter to enhance sky contrast</li>
        <li>Lightweight tripod for dawn/dusk shots</li>
      </ul>

      <blockquote>
        <p>"Patience and planning are key during sakura season. The fleeting nature of the blossoms makes each shot precious."</p>
      </blockquote>
    </div>
  </article>
</Layout>